The Secretary-General of the Central Committee of the Chinese Communist Party, the President of the State and the President of the Central Military Commission, Xi Jinping, will award the National Order and the National Honorary Medal to the recipients of the Order of the Republic, the Order of Friendship and the National Honorary Medal, respectively, and make important statements.
With the approval of the Central Committee of the Chinese Communist Party, the ceremony for the award of the National Order of the People ' s Republic of China and the State Honorary Honour will take place on 29 September at 10 a.m. in the People ' s Hall in Beijing.
